and Chetan Pulagam =E2=80=93 to trade Twilio options and stock in advance o=
f its May 6, 2020 earnings announcement while in possession of the confiden=
tial information concerning customer usage. According to the complaint, the=
 scheme generated more than $1 million in illegal trading profits.</p></blo=
ckquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That is from a Securities and Exchange=
