=80=9D=C2=A0</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Don=E2=80=99t do =
that, the options are how they catch you and the chats are how they prove i=
t, etc.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Still this is a little bit of a wei=
rd case. At one extreme of insider trading, if you work at a company and yo=
u find out that it is about to be acquired in a merger, and you buy a lot o=
